### Payment Service API Test File

### Process payment
POST http://localhost:8082/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "amount": 99.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111",
  "cardHolder": "John Doe",
  "expiryDate": "12/25",
  "cvv": "123"
}

### Get payment by ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/payments/1

### Get payment by transaction ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/payments/transaction/abc-123-def

### Get payment by order ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/payments/order/1

### Refund payment
POST http://localhost:8082/api/payments/1/refund

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health
